title: Bobby Planning ‘Gender Reveal’ + Lunchbox's Mind Blown At Starbucks + Chrissy Metz From 'This Is Us' Talks American Idol
itunes:title: Bobby Planning ‘Gender Reveal’ + Lunchbox's Mind Blown At Starbucks + Chrissy Metz From 'This Is Us' Talks American Idol
description:
Bobby announces he's planning a COVID 19 Antibodies results LIVE on Instagram much like a gender reveal. Be sure to follow him @mrbobbybones! Lunchbox goes to Starbucks to find out if items on their secret menu really exist. Plus, we talk with Chrissy Metz from “This Is Us” about her new music, acting and auditioning for American Idol!
